Coding Guidelines
+++++++++++++++++

Pascal S.P. Steger <psteger@phys.ethz.ch>

base: Kernighan & Ritchie
base: Linux Kernel Coding Style Guideline



* private variables have a "_" at the end
* parameters have the same name as private variables, but not "_"
* getVariable() and setVariable() for each variable that should be accessed from outside class

Research process
++++++++++++++++
* all halo-based extractions using C++, preferably in Halo.h
* analysis looking over all halos: MATLAB
* basic statistics: R
* visualization using S/M
* computations with analytical fitting, unit conversions in Mathematica
